	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-09-29T04:41:24">Bushveld Minerals Limited is a multi-commodity mineral development company. The principal activity of the Company is mineral project development focused on exploring and developing mineral of its portfolio of vanadium and titanium bearing iron ore and tin assets in Southern Africa. Its portfolio comprises the Bushveld Iron Ore Project, Bushveld Vanadium Project, Mokopane Tin Project and Marble Hall Tin Project, which are located on the northern limb of the Bushveld Complex, South Africa. It has three operating segments, which are Iron Ore exploration, Tin exploration and Coal exploration.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-12-14T03:49:32">BRIEF: For the six months ended 31 August 2015, Bushveld Minerals Limited revenues was not reported. Net loss decreased 31% to L847K. Lower net loss reflects Administrative expenses decrease of 43% to L955K (expense).</Text>
